doctype html
html(lang='en')

    head

        meta(charset='utf-8')
        meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no')
        meta(name='description', content='')
        meta(name='author', content='')

        title Heroic Features - Start Bootstrap Template

        // Favicon
        link(rel='icon', type='image/x-icon', href='assets/favicon.ico')

        // Bootstrap icons
        link(href='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.4.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css', rel='stylesheet')

        // Core theme CSS (includes Bootstrap)
        link(href='css/styles.css', rel='stylesheet')

    body

        // Responsive navbar
        nav.navbar.navbar-expand-lg.navbar-dark.bg-dark
            .container.px-lg-5
                a.navbar-brand(href='#!') Start Bootstrap
                button.navbar-toggler(type='button', data-bs-toggle='collapse', data-bs-target='#navbarSupportedContent', aria-controls='navbarSupportedContent', aria-expanded='false', aria-label='Toggle navigation')
                    span.navbar-toggler-icon
                #navbarSupportedContent.collapse.navbar-collapse
                    ul.navbar-nav.ms-auto.mb-2.mb-lg-0
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link.active(aria-current='page', href='#!') Home
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#!') About
                        li.nav-item
                            a.nav-link(href='#!') Contact
        // Header
        header.py-5
            .container.px-lg-5
                .p-4.p-lg-5.bg-light.rounded-3.text-center
                    .m-4.m-lg-5
                        h1.display-5.fw-bold A warm welcome!
                        p.fs-4
                            | Bootstrap utility classes are used to create this jumbotron since the old component has been removed from the framework. Why create custom CSS when you can use utilities?
                        a.btn.btn-primary.btn-lg(href='#!') Call to action

        // Page Content
        section.pt-4
            .container.px-lg-5
                // Page Features
                .row.gx-lg-5
                    .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4.mb-5
                        .card.bg-light.border-0.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center.p-4.p-lg-5.pt-0.pt-lg-0
                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-collection
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold Fresh new layout
                                p.mb-0 With Bootstrap 5, we've created a fresh new layout for this template!
                    .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4.mb-5
                        .card.bg-light.border-0.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center.p-4.p-lg-5.pt-0.pt-lg-0
                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-cloud-download
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold Free to download
                                p.mb-0 As always, Start Bootstrap has a powerful collectin of free templates.
                    .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4.mb-5
                        .card.bg-light.border-0.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center.p-4.p-lg-5.pt-0.pt-lg-0
                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-card-heading
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold Jumbotron hero header
                                p.mb-0 The heroic part of this template is the jumbotron hero header!
                    .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4.mb-5
                        .card.bg-light.border-0.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center.p-4.p-lg-5.pt-0.pt-lg-0
                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-bootstrap
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold Feature boxes
                                p.mb-0 We've created some custom feature boxes using Bootstrap icons!
                    .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4.mb-5
                        .card.bg-light.border-0.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center.p-4.p-lg-5.pt-0.pt-lg-0
                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-code
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold Simple clean code
                                p.mb-0 We keep our dependencies up to date and squash bugs as they come!
                    .col-lg-6.col-xxl-4.mb-5
                        .card.bg-light.border-0.h-100
                            .card-body.text-center.p-4.p-lg-5.pt-0.pt-lg-0
                                .feature.bg-primary.bg-gradient.text-white.rounded-3.mb-4.mt-n4
                                    i.bi.bi-patch-check
                                h2.fs-4.fw-bold A name you trust
                                p.mb-0 Start Bootstrap has been the leader in free Bootstrap templates since 2013!

        // Footer
        footer.py-5.bg-dark
            .container
                p.m-0.text-center.text-white Copyright &copy; Your Website 2022

        // Bootstrap core JS
        script(src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js')

        // Core theme JS
        script(src='js/scripts.js')